<table border="0" align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td>  
        
<p>
If <b>{data 'xxx'}</b> is used, then the data will not be processed before it is stored in the data store,<br>all above examples use it in this way.</p>
<p>If <b>{/data 'xxx'}</b> is used, then the data will be processed before it is stored in the data store.<br> Below a crazy example how this can be used: <br>
- first there is a JSON data definition<br>
- then this JSON data is converted to CSV data<br>
- then this CSV data is converted to XML data<br>
- then this XML data is converted to YAML data<br>
- then this YAML data is used to show a HTML table.

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

<p> 
  <table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
      
      
      
      <th bgcolor="#dddddd">HTML</th>
      <th bgcolor="#dddddd">RESULT</th>
    </tr>
    <tr><td style="vertical-align:top"><!-- START DEMO SOURCE --><pre><code style="color: #000000"><b>{<font color="blue">data </font><font color="red"><font color="black">'</font>myJson<font color="black">'</font></font>}</b>
  [ { "name": "bob",   "phone": "555-5555" },
    { "name": "jim",   "phone": "555-6666" },
    { "name": "joe",   "phone": "555-7777" },      
    { "name": "jerry", "phone": "555-8888" } ]
<b>{/<font color="blue">data</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>

<b>{<font color="blue">data</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
  name,phone
  <b>{<font color="blue">myJson</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
    <b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>name</font>}</b>, <b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>phone</font>}</b>
  <b>{/<font color="blue">myJson</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
<b>{/<font color="blue">data </font><font color="red"><font color="black">'</font>myCsv<font color="black">'</font></font>}</b>

<b>{<font color="blue">data</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
  &lt;records&gt;
    <b>{<font color="blue">myCsv</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
      &lt;record name="<b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>name</font>}</b>" phone="<b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>phone</font>}</b>"/&gt;
    <b>{/<font color="blue">myCsv</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
  &lt;/records&gt;
<b>{/<font color="blue">data </font><font color="red"><font color="black">'</font>myXml<font color="black">'</font></font>}</b>

<b>{<font color="blue">data</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
  ---
    <b>{<font color="blue">myXml</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
    - name: <b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>name</font>}</b>
      phone: <b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>phone</font>}</b>
    <b>{/<font color="blue">myXml</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
<b>{/<font color="blue">data </font><font color="red"><font color="black">'</font>myYaml<font color="black">'</font></font>}</b>

&lt;table border="1"&gt;
  <b>{<font color="blue">myYaml</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;<b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>name</font>}</b>&lt;/td&gt; 
      &lt;td&gt;<b>{<font color="green"><font color="red">$</font>phone</font>}</b>&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
  <b>{/<font color="blue">myYaml</font><font color="red"></font>}</b>
&lt;/table&gt;</code></pre><!-- END DEMO SOURCE --></td><td style="vertical-align:top"><code><span style="color: #000000"><!-- START DEMO RESULT --><table border="1">
  
    <tr>
      <td>bob</td> 
      <td>555-5555</td>
    </tr>
  
    <tr>
      <td>jim</td> 
      <td>555-6666</td>
    </tr>
  
    <tr>
      <td>joe</td> 
      <td>555-7777</td>
    </tr>
  
    <tr>
      <td>jerry</td> 
      <td>555-8888</td>
    </tr>
  
</table><!-- END DEMO RESULT --></span></code></td></tr>
  </table>
</p>